{"tid":2057144,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中三李同學：YOUNG LIVES MATTER","createTime":"2020-06-09T07:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T17:29:38.000Z","uid":1249,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c318c0330539b64dd0406ba62bfe1db4a59f779f","tid":2057144,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"中三李同學：想中共放手還返自由俾香港人<br />\n<br />\n今日是反修例運動 6.9 大遊行一周年，網民發起 7 區「和你 Lunch」，其中在中環有近 100 人參與，包括穿著校服、手舉「Young Lives Matter」標語的中三學生李同學。<br />\n<br />\n李同學表示一年前的今日開始參與運動，之後一直有出席大大小小的「和理非」抗爭活動，他曾身穿校服參與「和你 Lunch」被學校老師從新聞直播中認出，勸他不要再參加，但他反駁「我又冇犯法，點解唔可以參與」。<br />\n<br />\n對於反送中運動的前景，他不感悲觀，「只要堅持落去，就會有成功爭取嘅一日」，過去一年的警暴、國安法等「惡法」打壓年輕人的聲音，希望「Young Lives Matter」標語可以提醒香港人好好保護年輕人。<br />\n<br />\n於訪問尾聲，記者問李同學「你有咩夢想？」他堅定地答：「想中共放手，還返自由俾香港人」。<br />\n<br />\n攝／Oiyan Chan<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3U3uh3j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3U3uh3j.jpg&h=eec94f70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6bc79e262321b2eae14a81783001bff2bf5003a","tid":2057144,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:21:38.000Z","msg":"汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3155176744567924/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3155176744567924%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=2dc2c520\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3155176744567924/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"b915d64bbd43959b263152c5972014396b06cf8b","tid":2057144,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"young lives matter!"},{"pid":"7249d1c760f64f96b9440fec90cf79f64999adba","tid":2057144,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm